<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>红色文化数字展厅</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --font: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      --bg: #FAF8F0;               /* 象牙白背景 */
      --text-dark: #2B2B2B;        /* 深黑灰文字 */
      --accent-red: #C31A1E;       /* 红色强调 */
      --accent-gold: #D4AF37;      /* 金色点缀 */
      --glass-bg: rgba(255,255,255,.45);
      --glass-blur: 12px;
      --shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.12);
      --neumo-shadow: 4px 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.08), -4px -4px 12px rgba(255,255,255,.7);
      --transition: .3s ease-in-out;
    }
    *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
    html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
    body{font-family:var(--font);background:var(--bg);color:var(--text-dark);line-height:1.6;}
    a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none;}
    .section{opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);animation:fadeIn 0.6s forwards;}
    @keyframes fadeIn{to{opacity:1;transform:none;}}
    .section[data-delay]{animation-delay:calc(var(--delay)*0.15s);}
    .navbar{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:1000;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:1rem 2rem;background:var(--glass-bg);backdrop-filter:blur(var(--glass-blur));border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3);}
    .logo{font-weight:700;font-size:1.2rem;color:var(--accent-red);}
    .nav-links{display:flex;gap:1.5rem;}
    .nav-links a{position:relative;font-weight:600;transition:var(--transition);}
    .nav-links a::after{content:"";position:absolute;left:0;bottom:-3px;width:0;height:2px;background:var(--accent-gold);transition:var(--transition);}
    .nav-links a:hover::after{width:100%;}
    .nav-links a:hover{transform:scale(1.03);box-shadow:var(--shadow);}
    header{text-align:center;padding:4rem 1rem 2rem;}
    header h1{font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3rem);color:var(--accent-red);letter-spacing:.05em;}
    header h2{font-size:clamp(1rem,2.5vw,1.4rem);color:var(--text-dark);margin-top:.6rem;}
    .vlog{max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:2rem 1rem;}
    .vlog video{width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;display:block;border-radius:12px;background:var(--glass-bg);backdrop-filter:blur(var(--glass-blur));box-shadow:var(--shadow);transition:var(--transition);}
    .vlog video:hover{transform:scale(1.03) rotate(1deg);box-shadow:0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.2);}
    .vlog p{margin-top:1rem;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.6;color:#444;}
    .btn{display:inline-block;margin-top:1.5rem;padding:.8rem 1.6rem;background:var(--accent-red);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer;font-weight:600;box-shadow:var(--neumo-shadow);transition:var(--transition);}
    .btn:hover{transform:scale(1.03) rotate(-1deg);box-shadow:0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.2);}
    .carousel{display:flex;overflow-x:auto;gap:1rem;padding:0 1rem;scroll-snap-type:x mandatory;}
    .carousel img{flex:0 0 260px;max-width:100%;border-radius:12px;background:var(--glass-bg);backdrop-filter:blur(var(--glass-blur));box-shadow:var(--shadow);scroll-snap-align:center;transition:var(--transition);}
    .carousel img:hover{transform:scale(1.03);box-shadow:0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.2);}
    .intro{max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;padding:2rem 1rem;}
    .glass-card{background:var(--glass-bg);backdrop-filter:blur(var(--glass-blur));border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;box-shadow:var(--shadow);transition:var(--transition);}
    .glass-card:hover{transform:scale(1.02);box-shadow:0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.2);}
    .glass-card h3{font-size:1.8rem;color:var(--accent-red);margin-bottom:1rem;}
    .glass-card p{margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.7;}
    footer{background:#7A0C1C;color:#fff;text-align:center;padding:2rem 1rem;}
    footer .sep{width:80px;height:2px;background:var(--accent-gold);margin:1rem auto;}
    footer p{margin:.4rem 0;}
    footer .small{font-size:.85rem;opacity:.85;}
    .decor{position:fixed;top:0;right:0;pointer-events:none;width:250px;height:100vh;background:url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 200 200"><path fill="%23c31a1e" d="M0,100 C50,0 150,0 200,100 L200,200 L0,200 Z"/></svg>') no-repeat center/contain;animation:float 6s ease-in-out infinite;opacity:.15;}
    @keyframes float{0%,100%{transform:translateY(0);}50%{transform:translateY(-20px);}}
    @media(max-width:768px){.navbar{flex-direction:column;gap:.8rem;}.carousel img{flex:0 0 80%;}header{padding:3rem 0.5rem;}}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="decor"></div>
  <header class="navbar">
    <div class="logo">第二小组 · 红色研学展览</div>
    <nav class="nav-links">
      <a href="#vlog">Vlog</a>
      <a href="#wu_si">五四研学</a>
      <a href="#group_discussion">小组讨论</a>
      <a href="#labor_education">同劳教育</a>
      <a href="#summary">研学体会</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="section" data-delay="0">
    <header>
      <h1>寻访红色根脉，凝聚学风力量</h1>
      <h2>上海电机学院·第二小组 吴梦涵（组长） 王宇（督导）</h2>
    </header>
  </section>

  <section id="vlog" class="section vlog" data-delay="1">
    <video controls poster="./content.jpg"></video>
    <p>通过影像记录我们的研学之旅，从五四研学活动到小组讨论，再到同劳教育，每一段经历都值得回味。</p>
    <button class="btn">进入研学展区</button>
  </section>

  <section id="wu_si" class="section carousel-section" data-delay="2">
    <h3 class="section-title">五四研学</h3>
    <div class="carousel">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="五四研学照片1">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="五四研学照片2">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="五四研学照片3">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="五四研学照片4">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="五四研学照片5">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="五四研学照片6">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="五四研学照片7">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="五四研学照片8">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="五四研学照片9">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="五四研学照片10">
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="group_discussion" class="section carousel-section" data-delay="3">
    <h3 class="section-title">小组讨论</h3>
    <div class="carousel">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="小组讨论照片1">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="小组讨论照片2">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="小组讨论照片3">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="小组讨论照片4">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="小组讨论照片5">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="小组讨论照片6">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="小组讨论照片7">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="小组讨论照片8">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="小组讨论照片9">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="小组讨论照片10">
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="labor_education" class="section carousel-section" data-delay="4">
    <h3 class="section-title">同劳教育</h3>
    <div class="carousel">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="同劳教育照片1">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="同劳教育照片2">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="同劳教育照片3">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="同劳教育照片4">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="同劳教育照片5">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="同劳教育照片6">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="同劳教育照片7">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="同劳教育照片8">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="同劳教育照片9">
      <img src="./content.jpg" alt="同劳教育照片10">
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="summary" class="section intro" data-delay="5">
    <div class="glass-card">
      <h3>研学体会与感悟</h3>
      <p>本次红色研学活动以中华优秀传统文化和革命历史为主线，结合航海博物馆的实地考察、五四青年节纪念活动以及同劳实践，帮助同学们深化对红色精神的理解，提升实践能力和团队协作意识。</p>
      <p>在研学过程中，大家共同观看纪录片、进行现场互动、开展志愿服务，形成了“知史爱党、知行合一”的学习闭环。通过视频、图片和文字的多维呈现，期待更多人感受到研学的价值与魅力。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="section" data-delay="6">
    <div class="sep"></div>
    <p>组长：吴梦涵</p>
    <p>督导：王宇</p>
    <p>小组成员：罗梓杰&nbsp;&nbsp;（占位）</p>
    <p class="small">© 202X 上海电机学院·红色研学成果展示</p>
  </footer>

  <script>
    // 为 .section 添加递增的 data-delay（用于 staggered fade‑in）
    document.querySelectorAll('.section').forEach((s,i)=>s.dataset.delay=i);
  </script>
</body>
</html>
